title: Most googled car hire keywords in the United Kingdom ( UK ) in January 2016
summary: The Most googled Keywords in the hire keywords was rent_a_car , who made 933.1 thousands .
The most googled Keywords was car_hire_uk , with just 9.9 thousands .

In second place was Keywords car_rental with 40.5 thousands ; third place went to Keywords car_hire with 90.5 thousands ; fourth place went to Keywords Other_keywords with 933.1 thousands and fifth place went to Keywords rental_cars , who was 27.1 thousands .
gold: This statistic displays the most searched car hire and car rental related keywords on Google UK in January 2016 . Most popular was the term `` car hire `` , which was searched approximately 90.5 thousand times that month .
